videos.description: Minnesota's Reggie Lynch get rewarded for setting a screen with an easy dunk early in the game
videos.headline: Reggie Lynch with an early throwdown  at the rim

videos.description: Spartans Miles Bridges follows up the Matt McQuaid miss with a vicious tap dunk.
videos.headline: MSU's Bridges follows a miss for an amazing dunk

videos.description: Amir Coffey takes the ball off the curl and takes it to the rim for the two hand dunk.
videos.headline: Minnesota's Coffey drives to the lane and finishes

videos.description: After he missed a 3, Miles Bridges gets back in the play by getting up to finish a monster alley oop.
videos.headline: MSU's Alvin Ellis connects with Bridges.

videos.description: Akeem Springs hits a three pointer with four seconds left to put the Gophers up two going into the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Minnesota's Springs with a deep 3 to put the Gophers up 2 at the half

videos.description: Michigan State's Head Coach Tom Izzo breaks down what went right and what went wrong with Molly McGrath
videos.headline: Spartans Head Coach Tom Izzo discusses only being down two at halftime

videos.description: Miles Bridges gets the steal and puts on a show for the people of Washington DC.
videos.headline: MSU's Bridges nearly does a 360 dunk on breakaway

videos.description: Dupree McBrayer hits a deep three pointer to put the Gopher up eight.
videos.headline: Gophers McBrayer buries a deep three pointer

videos.description: After spinning off his defender, Miles Bridges finishes off the Matt McQuaid pass at the rim.
videos.headline: Miles Bridges gets free to attack the rim.

videos.description: Minnesota gets a late lead as Reggie Lynch attacks the rim after executing the pick and roll.
videos.headline: Gophers' Lynch attacks the rim
